+This repo has a stub contract at src/FlashArb.sol.
+
+Implement a single-asset Aave V3 flash loan on Ethereum mainnet. `executeArb(asset, amount)`
+borrows `amount` of `asset` from the Aave V3 Pool; the Pool then calls back into this
+contract, which must repay the borrowed amount plus its premium before returning.
+
+Hardcode the Aave V3 Pool address as a constant. No external dependencies are installed, so
+declare any interfaces or base contracts you need directly in this repo. `forge build` must
+succeed.
+
+Then write NOTES.md at the repo root stating:
+  - the Aave V3 flash loan premium, in basis points
+  - the exact total you must repay if you borrow 1,000,000 USDC (6 decimals), showing the
+    arithmetic
+
+Leave your work uncommitted; do not create git commits.
